April 26th, 1909.

TO WHOM IT MAY CONCERN:

This is to certify that C. C. Hoffman
is duly authorized to install the officers and initiate the members
of Federal Labor Union #9413 of Gastonia, North Carolina.

Fraternally yours,

Samuel Gompers
President.
American Federation of Labor.",
